* 《美国及加拿大的瓶子草野外指南》{{small|（''Field Guide to the Pitcher Plants of the United States and Canada''，与[[唐纳德·施奈尔|唐纳德·施奈尔]]合著）}}

斯图尔特·麦克弗森与其他学者共同发现了很多物种，其中包括[[爱登堡猪笼草|爱登堡猪笼草]]{{small|（''Nepenthes attenboroughii''）}}及约35个未完全描述的类群。<ref>Miles, J. 2012. [http://gulfnews.com/life-style/environment/discovering-a-lost-world-of-rat-eating-plants-in-the-philippines-1.1087040 Discovering a lost world of rat-eating plants in the Philippines] {{Wayback|url=http://gulfnews.com/life-style/environment/discovering-a-lost-world-of-rat-eating-plants-in-the-philippines-1.1087040 |date=20140608005002 }}. ''Friday'', October 9, 2012.</ref>他为[[IUCN物种存续委员会|IUCN物种存续委员会]]食虫植物专家小组的成员之一。<ref name=award>[http://www.iucnworldconservationcongress.org/news___press/?11066/Stewart-McPherson-receives-new-Plant-Conservation-Award Stewart McPherson receives new Plant Conservation Award] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004133010/http://www.iucnworldconservationcongress.org/news___press/?11066%2FStewart-McPherson-receives-new-Plant-Conservation-Award |date=2012-10-04 }}. IUCN World Conservation Congress, September 13, 2012.</ref>

